title: Sewa Kroetkov Rides Ricta Slix!
description: Grind Faster – Grind Longer! The revolution in skateboard wheel technology continues... Ricta Slix combine the NRG Formula, proven THE fastest urethane in skateboarding, with a custom molded TPU slide insert for three times more slip and minimal drag on the inside of the wheel for longer and faster grinds. 81b is hard and fast!
